**Professional Profile**
Đoàn Thống Lĩnh is an accomplished Backend Developer with 2 years of experience, including leadership roles on significant projects. They specialize in developing robust, cross-platform applications, demonstrated through projects like library management, e-commerce, and educational platforms. Their expertise encompasses implementing complex functionalities such as user authentication, product catalogs, and real-time features, often leading frontend-backend integration.

**Core Skills & Technology**
Proficient in key backend technologies including Python, Node.js, and Java, complemented by strong database skills in MongoDB, MySQL, Firebase, and SQL Server. Experienced with RESTful APIs, Microservices architecture, and Agile/Scrum methodologies, utilizing Git for version control.

**Education & Certifications**
Currently pursuing a Bachelor of Software Engineering at Ton Duc Thang University. Holds an English APTIS Level B1 (CEFR) certification and has completed an Agile Development & Scrum Framework Course.